Author: sweatyandsweet
Text: I forced myself to eat breakfast before my exams (all were morning ones) so that I could concentrate and also so that stomach didn't growl loudly whilst taking the exam. I also walked to and from my exams. Getting your blood pumping can improve focus, just take it easy and don't overdo it because if you are restricting heavily you may get dizzy or collapse.
